io.confluent.support.metrics

Class PhoneHomeConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.support.metrics.BaseSupportConfig
      • io.confluent.support.metrics.PhoneHomeConfig

  • public class PhoneHomeConfig
extends BaseSupportConfig
    Use this config for component-specific phone-home clients. It disables writing metrics to Kafka topic and ensures that non-test customer Ids are "anonymous", even if the client sets support topic and customer id in the config. standard phone-home libraries (the difference is a different URI format).
